{"tid":1628392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔幾時先走出平行時空","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:24:33.000Z","uid":123633,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46f211f7883c48f8d69200f7fef2110436ee01db","tid":1628392,"uid":123633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"尋日無啦啦呼籲全民休息日<br />\n但係出面都好多人遊行<br />\n<br />\n今日明明講好去港島<br />\n無啦啦又叫人去九龍<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野叫做黨鐵落閘返唔到屋企<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4個月啦 當勇武CONDOM呀？</span></strong><br />\n你班分化撚睇死都係和理非，返唔到屋企都瓜瓜嘈，有無諗過入過新屋嶺嘅手足呀？咪撚再咁自私啦！<br />\n<br />\n我住大西北，今日會去港島，人多先有noise 一直都係咁！推完緊急法居然無超大型遊行，對家笑緊你咋！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日去港島！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8fb8244d4ff311c5e57ef9dda08672e6d73f090f","tid":1628392,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"日日一起身見到比人推爆既post都係spin風向post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71402b7f352e7d8da0a65f2266b37931c42faa39","tid":1628392,"uid":123633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b522046365403256717cf5b096cd1a6b8ead477","tid":1628392,"uid":277589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"所以呢排都少上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc91c3017a85a9dd1e6cf4f91efd1af36bd9475","tid":1628392,"uid":267277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"今日有行動呀，邊有休息日<br />\n一停就玩完架啦！"},{"pid":"f9d3d06588d53bc3865b4427df9316764a2b7b65","tid":1628392,"uid":20101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"冇黨鐵番唔到 依家仲諗黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/